name: MTLLibraryError.Code
desc: Error codes returned by Metal for library errors.

items.name: case unsupported
items.desc: Metal couldn’t support the requested action.

items.name: case `internal`
items.desc: The action caused an internal error.

items.name: case compileFailure
items.desc: The library or function failed to compile.

items.name: case compileWarning
items.desc: The library or function compiled successfully but generated warnings.

items.name: case fileNotFound
items.desc: Metal couldn’t find the Metal source file.

items.name: case functionNotFound
items.desc: Metal couldn’t find the specified Metal function.
